OL,3,C'Funny, kind with a huge heart':
OL,4,CTribute to dad of two killed by HGV on
OL,5,Cmotorway
OL,7,FThe family of a dad of two who died
OL,8,Fafter being hit by a HGV on the M57
OL,9,Fmotorway say he was "funny, kind and
OL,10,Fhad a huge heart" and they will "miss
OL,11,Fhim forever".
OL,13,FSteven Moglione, 48, died on the M57
OL,14,Fon Merseyside on on Saturday 20 April.
OL,16,FEmergency services were contacted just
OL,17,Fbefore 3.45am following reports that a
OL,18,Fman had been involved in a collision
OL,19,Fwith a HGV on the Northbound side of
OL,20,Fthe motorway between junctions 2 and 3.
