OL,3,C'Funny, kind with a huge heart':
OL,4,CTribute to dad of two killed by HGV on
OL,5,Cmotorway
OL,7,FThe driver of the HGV stopped at the
OL,8,Fscene and assisted detectives in
OL,9,Funderstanding the full circumstances
OL,10,Fof what happened.
OL,12,FSteven's family have now issued the
OL,13,Ffollowing statement: "This has come as
OL,14,Fa huge shock to the family who are
OL,15,Fcurrently comforting each other at
OL,16,Fthis extremely hard time.
OL,18,F"Steven will be deeply missed by all
OL,19,Fof his family and friends, he was a
OL,20,Fdevoted husband, father, son, brother
OL,21,F& uncle a true family man.
