OL,3,C'Funny, kind with a huge heart':
OL,4,CTribute to dad of two killed by HGV on
OL,5,Cmotorway
OL,7,F"Steven was funny, kind and had a huge
OL,8,Fheart, he was loved by everyone who
OL,9,Fmet him.
OL,11,F"His wife, two children and family
OL,12,Fwill miss him forever but will be
OL,13,Feternally grateful for the love and
OL,14,Ffun times they have shared together".
OL,16,FThe motorway was closed for 15 hours
OL,17,Fafter the crash.
