OL,7,FDetective Sergeant Kurt Timpson, Lead
OL,8,FInvestigating Officer from the
OL,9,FMerseyside Police Serious Collision
OL,10,FInvestigation Unit said: "My thoughts
OL,11,Fremain with Steven's family at this
OL,12,Fsad time.
OL,14,F"They are being supported by specially
OL,15,Ftrained Police Officers. I would ask
OL,16,Fthat they are now allowed the time and
OL,17,Fprivacy to comes to terms with their
OL,18,Floss.
