OL,3,C'Funny, kind with a huge heart':
OL,4,CTribute to dad of two killed by HGV on
OL,5,Cmotorway
OL,7,F"I would like to appeal to anyone who
OL,8,Fwas on the M57 Northbound at the time
OL,9,Fof this collision to please get in
OL,10,Ftouch.
OL,12,F"We know from initial enquiries that
OL,13,Fseveral other vehicles passed through
OL,14,Fthis area just after the collision and
OL,15,Fit is extremely important that we
OL,16,Fspeak with those drivers, even if they
OL,17,Fdid not physically witness the
OL,18,Fcollision.
