OL,3,C'Funny, kind with a huge heart':
OL,4,CTribute to dad of two killed by HGV on
OL,5,Cmotorway
OL,7,F"The vehicle involved was a DAF Heavy
OL,8,FGoods Vehicle and the collision
OL,9,Fhappened at 3.40am on Saturday morning.
OL,11,F"Please can motorists check their
OL,12,Fdashcams. Front and rear cameras can
OL,13,Foften record vital evidence, unbeknown
OL,14,Fto the driver. Any information however
OL,15,Fsmall it may seem could prove vital to
OL,16,Four enquiries.
