OL,3,C'Funny, kind with a huge heart':
OL,4,CTribute to dad of two killed by HGV on
OL,5,Cmotorway
OL,7,F"I would also like to thank motorists
OL,8,Fand members of the local community for
OL,9,Ftheir patience and understanding as It
OL,10,Fwas necessary to close the M57 in both
OL,11,Fdirections until late into Saturday
OL,12,Fevening.
OL,14,F"I appreciate the difficulty this
OL,15,Fcaused and can assure people that this
OL,16,Fwas unavoidable due to the nature of
OL,17,Fthis tragic incident."
